{"id":86218,"title":"Integrating social work into palliative care for lung cancer patients and families: a multidimensional approach.","abstract":"Lung cancer patients and their family caregivers face a wide range of potentially distressing symptoms across the four domains of quality of life. A multidimensional approach to addressing these complex concerns with early integration of palliative care has proven beneficial. This article highlights opportunities to integrate social work using a comprehensive quality of life model and a composite patient scenario from a large lung cancer educational intervention National Cancer Institute-funded program project grant. ","date":"2014-07-03","categories":"Respiratory Tract Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24797998","annotations":[{"name":"Quality of life","weight":0.796625,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quality_of_life"},{"name":"Palliative care","weight":0.646624,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Palliative_care"},{"name":"Cancer","weight":0.636415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cancer"},{"name":"Lung","weight":0.608877,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lung"},{"name":"Lung cancer","weight":0.571231,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lung_cancer"},{"name":"Education","weight":0.511853,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Education"},{"name":"Caregiver","weight":0.502464,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caregiver"},{"name":"Social work","weight":0.469821,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Social_work"},{"name":"Patient","weight":0.369579,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient"},{"name":"Symptom","weight":0.367494,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Symptom"},{"name":"Model (person)","weight":0.0554043,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Model_(person)"},{"name":"Face","weight":0.0391252,"wikipedia_article":"http://en